lead_paragraph: American Lexi Thompson's putter switch helped her surge up the leaderboard to grab a share of the lead at the halfway mark of the ANA Inspiration in Rancho Mirage, California on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Putter Changes Helps Thompson to Share of ANA Inspiration Lead
